I was wrong about Primer in the way I was wrong about a lot of companies ba=
ck in 2020-2022, and in the way I think a lot of investors are still wrong:=
 I thought that software (a clearly superior business model) was a better a=
pproach than rebuilding the entire product, atoms and all. That you might r=
